Martius
</taxonomicName>
) forest, in an area of rainforest and Cerrado vegetation (
<bibRefCitation author="Carvalho-Filho, F. S. &amp; Sousa, J. R. P. &amp; Esposito, M. C." box="[625,929,295,321]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" pagination="349 - 353" refId="ref105208" refString="Carvalho-Filho, F. S., Sousa, J. R. P. &amp; Esposito, M. C. (2017) A new species and new records of Oxysarcodexia Townsend (Diptera: Sarcophagidae) from Brazil. Revista Brasileira de Entomologia, 61 (4), 349 - 353. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / j. rbe. 2017.07.005" type="journal article" year="2017">
